36:["$","p",null,{"className":"border-t mt-8 pt-6 text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center","children":"Vraman Holidays™ is a Nepal-based destination management company dedicated to helping travellers experience Nepal and the world in meaningful ways. We do not simply arrange trips – we create stories worth living, memories worth sharing, and experiences worth remembering. Every itinerary, every adventure, and every journey is designed with one purpose: to help our guests confidently Propose Your Destination™ while we take care of the rest."}]
